year variable converter

Source: R/tges.R
year_variable_converter.Rd

for the 1999-2003 tges files, the 'year' of the data was encoded in the variable names

Usage

year_variable_converter(df, end_year)

Arguments

df

a tges indicator data frame published between 1999 and 2003

end_year

year published

Value

data frame that conforms to 2004-2009 style
